##The six words in the epidemic affect us all

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Long Hui, thepaper.cn

When the epidemic is over, we are likely to forget some of the details, but we will still remember clearly the emotions and perceptions of today, and may soon reconnect with the past. In this epidemic there are six words to give you and me a new understanding and understanding, affecting all aspects of our time, these words or abstract, but also specific.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
1: Unprecedented closure of the city, the formation of a huge physical division, the city, the countryside, residential areas of each other organic cut, blocking People's Daily Travel, logistics. The connections that are made over the Internet, but at the same time face an invisible virtual blockade.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
2 trapped: We are trapped in a semi-enclosed space, some people began to remote network office, network classroom, they have mixed with life.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
3 Ballad: In the way of Communication has changed profoundly today, society has entered the stage of information overload, a variety of plausible rumors in the network to obtain a living space. It's hard to tell which is reliable information and which is a rumor.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
4 Rob: Mask, disinfectant, Shuanghuanglian, vegetables and even toilet paper... ? ... What caused our blind panic buying?

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
5 Masks: Although the average daily production of masks has risen from 20 million a year ago to more than 100 million a day. According to the current demand after the resumption of work, there is still a huge gap.

6 Assistance: The arrival of a medical team of forty thousand people from all over the country, a steady stream of medical supplies and daily necessities in the hard hit areas, is the key to the rapid and effective control of the epidemic.
